Inside the function wait_on_page_bit there is this code:
	...
if (test_bit(bit_nr, &page->flags)) {
	sync_page(page);
	io_schedule();
}
	...
If I move the io_schedule() before sync_page(page), this will improve the 
response time of interactive applications?
